### ── DELIVERY SERVICE (/deliveries) ────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Ön koşul: orderId için sales.http → createOrder; ödeme tamamlanmış olmalı.

### 1. Teslimat planla — Manager
### orderId: sales.http'deki createOrder'dan dönen ID
# @name scheduleDelivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/scheduleDelivery
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ORDER_ID",
  "plannedDate": "2026-07-15"
}

### 2. Teslimatları listele — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/Deliveries
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Teslimatları listele — Customer Bauer (sadece kendi siparişinin teslimatı)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/Deliveries
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Teslimat güncelle — tarih ve durum değiştir
### deliveryId: 1. adımdan dönen ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/updateDelivery
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryId": "BURAYA_DELIVERY_ID",
  "plannedDate": "2026-07-16",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### 5. Teslimatı tamamla — DELIVERED
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/completeDelivery
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deliveryId": "BURAYA_DELIVERY_ID"
}

### 6. Teslimat planla — Customer rolüyle (reddedilmeli — Manager/Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliveries/scheduleDelivery
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ORDER_ID",
  "plannedDate": "2026-07-20"
}